---
// WhyClientsTrustUs section - displays core credibility drivers with 2x2 card grid
---

<section class="why-clients-trust-us" aria-label="Why clients trust GST">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="trust-content">
      <h2 class="brutal-heading-lg">Why Clients Trust GST</h2>

      <div class="trust-cards">
        <div class="trust-card brutal-frosted">
          <h3>Independent, vendor-neutral guidance</h3>
          <p>
            No technology bias, no vendor relationships, no hidden agendas. GST's recommendations
            are grounded in your strategic objectives and technical realities, not product portfolio
            incentives.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-card brutal-frosted">
          <h3>Technical depth, business clarity</h3>
          <p>
            GST bridges the gap between technical architecture and business impact. Complex systems
            become clear. Trade-offs get quantified. Risk becomes actionable.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-card brutal-frosted">
          <h3>Executive-ready outputs</h3>
          <p>
            Technical findings translated for boards and C-suite. No jargon. Clear implications.
            Decision-ready context that informs strategy and allocation.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-card brutal-frosted">
          <h3>Shovel-ready initiatives</h3>
          <p>
            Every recommendation accounts for budget, timeline, and team capacity. Roadmaps that
            actually happen. Next steps teams can execute.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* Component styles following design system patterns */
  .why-clients-trust-us {
    padding: var(--spacing-3xl) 0;
    background: transparent;
    position: relative;
  }

  .trust-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .brutal-heading-lg {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .trust-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--gap-extra-wide);
  }

  .trust-card {
    padding: var(--spacing-2xl);
    background: transparent;
    border: 2px solid light-dark(var(--border-light), var(--border-dark-default));
    border-radius: 0;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-normal);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .trust-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .trust-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-family: monospace;
    font-weight: var(--font-weight-bold);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .trust-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-family: monospace;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
    flex-grow: 1;
  }

  /* Responsive design */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .trust-cards {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: var(--gap-wide);
    }

    .trust-card {
      padding: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .trust-card h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }

    .trust-card p {
      font-size: var(--text-small);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .why-clients-trust-us {
      padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
    }

    .brutal-heading-lg {
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
    }

    .trust-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--gap-normal);
    }

    .trust-card {
      padding: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .trust-card h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
    }

    .trust-card p {
      font-size: var(--text-small);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .why-clients-trust-us {
      padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    }

    .brutal-heading-lg {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .trust-cards {
      gap: var(--gap-normal);
    }

    .trust-card {
      padding: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .trust-card h3 {
      font-size: var(--text-small);
      margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
      text-align: center;
    }

    .trust-card p {
      font-size: var(--text-tiny);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  }
</style>
